{
  "stem": "17001.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So this was the introduction to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then next morning, as we are standing out-- in the meantime, we were standing against the-- the side of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's the way we were sleeping standing up, because by that time we were so exhausted that we were sleeping standing up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went out next morning, standing on [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of this beautiful woman with red, long hair, with white skin like cream, she start to speak in German.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She said, you lousy this and this and this and this and this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see that chimney over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's where your mother and your family been through, right through that-- the smoke.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The smoke you see, that's them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They are just coming got.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You came through the gate on your feet, but you're going to go out that way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I looked at my sister and I said, that's a nice welcome, that this is a real crazy place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then what happened with-- as time was going by, I-- I got to look around and I see this one, I see that one.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then a few days later, I had met my cousin who I used to go to school together from Kisvarda, because they came with the first transport to-- to this place.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I find out the name of the place was Auschwitz, Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when I met her, we hugged and we kissed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said to her, whom are you with?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, we are here and we would like you should come with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She said, oh, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She said, I'm staying with my friends and we are together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I said to her, you are foolish, because we are your blood relative.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, why-- why do you stay with your friends?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
